Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.45,0:22:11.67,EDJP2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)\blur3}Right in front of me, all the stars that take the sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.67,0:22:17.51,EDJP2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)\blur3}a million lights surround me with their soft embrace
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.51,0:22:23.34,EDJP2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)\blur3}あの頃　信じてた世界は
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.34,0:22:29.68,EDJP2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)\blur3}今もまだ正しいかな
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.31,0:22:35.99,EDJP2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)\blur3}I know for certain now
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.99,0:22:42.74,EDJP2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)\blur3}彷徨う僕たちは
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.74,0:22:46.37,EDJP2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)\blur3}手探りでも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.74,0:22:52.01,EDJP2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)\blur3}愛を感じたい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.01,0:22:57.67,EDJP2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)\blur3}Oh all the visions living in your memory,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.67,0:23:03.59,EDJP2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)\blur3}Will you remember me as you loved me？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.59,0:23:10.14,EDJP2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)\blur3}どんな形でも　代わりはないから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.14,0:23:14.90,EDJP2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)\blur3}キミとなら紡げる Love Story
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.23,0:23:23.90,EDJP2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)\blur3}微笑み合う日を重ねたい
Dialogue: 1,0:22:05.45,0:22:11.67,EDCN2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)\blur3}繁星就在眼前  铺满整片夜空
Dialogue: 1,0:22:11.67,0:22:17.51,EDCN2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)\blur3}无数光芒将我拥入怀中
Dialogue: 1,0:22:17.51,0:22:23.34,EDCN2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)\blur3}曾经笃信的理想世界
Dialogue: 1,0:22:23.34,0:22:29.68,EDCN2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)\blur3}如今是否还处于正轨
Dialogue: 1,0:22:30.31,0:22:35.99,EDCN2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)\blur3}此刻我已经确信
Dialogue: 1,0:22:35.99,0:22:42.74,EDCN2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)\blur3}彷徨无助的我们
Dialogue: 1,0:22:42.74,0:22:46.37,EDCN2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)\blur3}哪怕不断摸索
Dialogue: 1,0:22:46.74,0:22:52.01,EDCN2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)\blur3}也要触碰爱的温度
Dialogue: 1,0:22:52.01,0:22:57.67,EDCN2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)\blur3}记忆深处  景象万千
Dialogue: 1,0:22:57.67,0:23:03.59,EDCN2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)\blur3}可还记得  你曾深爱的我
Dialogue: 1,0:23:03.59,0:23:10.14,EDCN2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)\blur3}无论何种形态  终是无可替代
Dialogue: 1,0:23:10.14,0:23:14.90,EDCN2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)\blur3}与你携手  才能织成爱的诗篇
